---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-warm">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12" data-reveal>
      <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-secondary mb-4">How It Works</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-primary leading-tight">
        How we start working together
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" data-reveal-stagger>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-lg font-bold mb-4">1</div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-primary mb-2">Discovery call</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">30 minutes. We discuss what's not working, what you need, and whether there's a fit. No pitch, no pressure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-lg font-bold mb-4">2</div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-primary mb-2">Custom proposal</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Within 48 hours, you get a scope of work with the recommended tier, deliverables, and timeline.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-lg font-bold mb-4">3</div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-primary mb-2">Onboarding</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Week 1: I audit your current systems, meet key stakeholders, and build the operating rhythm.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-lg font-bold mb-4">4</div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-primary mb-2">Running</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">By week 3-4, your operations are proactive instead of reactive. You stop being your own EA.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-10" data-reveal>
      <a
        href={`${base}contact`}
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-secondary text-white px-7 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-secondary/90 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-secondary/20"
      >
        Book a Discovery Call
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
